name: Paw Puppy Patrol - Jumpy Dog Adventure
name_original: Paw Puppy Patrol - Jumpy Dog Adventure
description:
Absolutely FREE and super fun adventure!

Compete with your FRIENDS and beat the world record!

Pole vault from land to land
Avoid the patrol birds
Do not jump on the bombs
Catch the parrot and get an extra life!

Maybe you will be on the top of the leaderboard! Become the dog master - Paw Puppy Patrol wants your help!

Paw Puppy Patrol - Jumpy Dog Adventure is waiting for you!
